---
title: "Error Handling & Resilience — State Machine"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> RequestReceived: POST /v1/chat/completions

    RequestReceived: Request Received by Orchestrator

    %% ─── Guard Service Failures ───
    state guard_input <<choice>>
    RequestReceived --> guard_input: Call Guard (input)

    guard_input --> GuardOK_Input: Response received
    guard_input --> GuardDown_Input: Unreachable / Timeout

    GuardDown_Input: Guard Unreachable (Input)
    note right of GuardDown_Input
        Policy: FAIL CLOSED
        Treat as unsafe → return apology
        Timeout: GUARD_TIMEOUT_S (10s)
    end note
    GuardDown_Input --> Apology

    state guard_parse_input <<choice>>
    GuardOK_Input --> guard_parse_input: Parse response

    guard_parse_input --> InputSafe: label = "safe"
    guard_parse_input --> Apology: label = "unsafe"
    guard_parse_input --> GuardUnparseable_Input: Cannot parse

    GuardUnparseable_Input: Guard Output Unparseable (Input)
    note right of GuardUnparseable_Input
        Policy: FAIL CLOSED
        Treat as unsafe → return apology
        Log error for debugging
    end note
    GuardUnparseable_Input --> Apology

    %% ─── Embedding Service Failures ───
    InputSafe: Input Safe → Proceed

    state embed_check <<choice>>
    InputSafe --> embed_check: Call Embedding Service

    embed_check --> EmbedOK: Response received
    embed_check --> EmbedDown: Unreachable / Timeout

    EmbedDown: Embedding Service Unreachable
    note right of EmbedDown
        Policy: HTTP 503
        "Service Unavailable"
        Timeout: EMBEDDING_TIMEOUT_S (15s)
        Cannot proceed without embeddings
    end note
    EmbedDown --> HTTP503

    %% ─── Qdrant Failures ───
    EmbedOK: Embedding OK → Retrieve

    state qdrant_check <<choice>>
    EmbedOK --> qdrant_check: Query Qdrant

    qdrant_check --> QdrantOK: Results returned
    qdrant_check --> QdrantEmpty: 0 results
    qdrant_check --> QdrantDown: Unreachable

    QdrantDown: Qdrant Unreachable
    note right of QdrantDown
        Policy: HTTP 503
        "Service Unavailable"
    end note
    QdrantDown --> HTTP503

    QdrantEmpty: Qdrant Returns 0 Results
    note right of QdrantEmpty
        Policy: Return "no context" message
        "Xin lỗi, tôi không thể tìm thấy
        thông tin liên quan."
        Skip LLM call entirely
    end note
    QdrantEmpty --> NoContext

    %% ─── Reranker Failures ───
    QdrantOK: Qdrant OK → Rerank

    state rerank_check <<choice>>
    QdrantOK --> rerank_check: Call Reranker

    rerank_check --> RerankOK: Scores returned
    rerank_check --> RerankDown: Unreachable / Timeout

    RerankDown: Reranker Unreachable
    note right of RerankDown
        Policy: GRACEFUL DEGRADATION
        Fall back to raw retrieval order
        Log warning
        Continue pipeline
        Timeout: RERANKER_TIMEOUT_S (15s)
    end note
    RerankDown --> WebFallbackEval: Use raw retrieval order

    RerankOK: Reranker OK
    RerankOK --> WebFallbackEval

    %% ─── Tavily Failures ───
    WebFallbackEval: Web Fallback Evaluation

    state tavily_check <<choice>>
    WebFallbackEval --> tavily_check: If fallback triggered

    tavily_check --> TavilyOK: Results returned
    tavily_check --> TavilyDown: Unavailable / Error
    tavily_check --> SkipTavily: Not triggered

    TavilyDown: Tavily Unavailable
    note right of TavilyDown
        Policy: GRACEFUL DEGRADATION
        Log warning
        Proceed with existing Qdrant chunks
        Do NOT abort request
    end note
    TavilyDown --> BuildPrompt: Use existing chunks

    TavilyOK: Tavily OK
    TavilyOK --> BuildPrompt: Merged context

    SkipTavily: Fallback Not Needed
    SkipTavily --> BuildPrompt

    %% ─── LLM Failures ───
    BuildPrompt: Build Prompt → Call LLM

    state llm_check <<choice>>
    BuildPrompt --> llm_check: Call LLM

    llm_check --> LLMOK: Answer generated
    llm_check --> LLMDown: Unreachable / Timeout
    llm_check --> LLMMalformed: Empty/malformed output

    LLMDown: LLM Unreachable / Timeout
    note right of LLMDown
        Policy: HTTP 503
        "Service Unavailable"
        Timeout: LLM_TIMEOUT_S (60s)
    end note
    LLMDown --> HTTP503

    LLMMalformed: LLM Empty/Malformed Output
    note right of LLMMalformed
        Policy: Return apology
        Log error for debugging
    end note
    LLMMalformed --> Apology

    %% ─── Output Guard Failures ───
    LLMOK: LLM OK → Output Guard

    state guard_output_check <<choice>>
    LLMOK --> guard_output_check: Call Guard (output)

    guard_output_check --> OutputGuardOK: Response received
    guard_output_check --> GuardDown_Output: Unreachable

    GuardDown_Output: Guard Unreachable (Output)
    note right of GuardDown_Output
        Policy: FAIL CLOSED
        Treat as unsafe → return apology
    end note
    GuardDown_Output --> Apology

    OutputGuardOK: Output Guard Response
    note right of OutputGuardOK
        Safe → deliver answer
        Unsafe → retry once → safe or apology
        Unparseable → treat as unsafe
    end note
    OutputGuardOK --> DeliverAnswer: Safe path
    OutputGuardOK --> Apology: Unsafe after retry

    %% ─── Terminal States ───
    DeliverAnswer: ✅ Deliver Answer + Citations
    DeliverAnswer --> [*]

    Apology: ⚠️ Return Apology Message
    note right of Apology
        APOLOGY_MESSAGE env var
        Used for guardrail failures only
    end note
    Apology --> [*]

    HTTP503: 🔴 HTTP 503 Service Unavailable
    note right of HTTP503
        Used for infrastructure failures
        Distinct from guardrail apology
        WebUI shows "service unavailable"
    end note
    HTTP503 --> [*]

    NoContext: 📭 No Context Found
    note right of NoContext
        "Xin lỗi, tôi không thể tìm thấy
        thông tin liên quan."
        No LLM call made
    end note
    NoContext --> [*]
